Hangman

a basic (socket)networked 2 player hangman game

game.py
-contains base game object as well as objects for the status messages and 1:1 matchup

sserver.py
-basic game server
-goal for 2 player game is players trade words then race to finish

play_client.py (optional host/port argument to inidicate where server is)
-makes connection to the game server and decodes/encodes game status json objects to communicate with server
-user can select 1 or 2 player game


Features Snazzy Ascii graphics:

